 processing facilities that are accessed, processed, communicated to, or
 managed by external parties
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\shape up
The risks to the organization's information and information processing facilitie
s from business processes involving external parties should be identified
 and appropriate controls implemented before granting access.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\shape up
